messages.message:
Hello all, Instabase's Design team is currently organizing user testing and research sessions from *Jan 2-5* to enhance the user experience on AI Hub. We're seeking 30-45 minutes of your time for individual task-based testing sessions. If you're interested in participating, please inform us!

Each session will involve completing tasks on AI Hub while we observe, allowing us to pinpoint areas of success and improvement in the product.

cc: @Jianqi Xing @Siya @Natasha @tj.serkes
